### 1. Login to get the JWT token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test-player@nightcity.com",
  "password": "supersecurepassword"
}

### Store the token from the login response
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 2. Generate Today's AI Daily Plan
POST http://localhost:3000/api/plans/generate-today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get generated Daily Plan
GET http://localhost:3000/api/plans/today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json